response.title: Hilton Sibiu
response.description: Understated hotel featuring a gym, a bar & 3 restaurants, plus an indoor pool & a spa with saunas.
response.hotelDescription:
Nestled in Dumbrava Sibiului Natural Park, this understated hotel is 6 km from The Bridge of Lies and 5 km from the Franz Binder Museum of Universal Ethnography.
 Formal rooms and suites offer free Wi-Fi, flat-screen TVs and minifridges, plus marble bathrooms and balconies. Some have sitting areas and/or sofabeds. Upgraded quarters offer access to a club lounge with complimentary breakfast, snacks and drinks.
 Amenities include 3 restaurants, a bar, and meeting and event space. Other amenities include a gym, a gift shop and an indoor pool. There's also a spa with saunas, and meditation and steam rooms. Breakfast and parking are available.

response.title: Continental Forum
response.subTitle: Hotel Continental Forum Sibiu
response.description: Refined lodging in a restored 1800s building with a restaurant, a bar & a cafe.
response.hotelDescription:
In a leafy commercial area, this elegant hotel in a restored 19th-century building is a 7-minute walk from the Brukenthal National Museum and a 9-minute walk from the Council Tower of Sibiu.
 Warmly decorated rooms provide free Wi-Fi, flat-screen TVs, safes and minibars. Suites add living rooms. A 2-bedroom penthouse apartment has a kitchen and a whirlpool tub. Room service is available 24/7.
 A breakfast buffet (fee) is served in an airy restaurant that has a garden. There's a relaxed cafe and a bar, as well as a gym and a spa area.

response.title: Mercure
response.subTitle: Mercure Hotel Sibiu Airport
response.description: Casual airport hotel offering a restaurant & a lobby bar, plus a fitness center & a sauna.
response.hotelDescription:
In an area filled with business parks, this laid-back airport hotel is 4 km from the Council Tower and 5 km from the Brukenthal National Museum. Sibiu International Airport is 2 km away.
 Warmly decorated rooms, some with sloped ceilings, offer Wi-Fi, flat-screens and minifridges, plus sitting areas. Suites feature sofabeds.
 There's a chic lobby bar and a restaurant, as well as a terrace and meeting space. Other amenities include a sauna and a gym. Parking, an airport shuttle and a breakfast buffet are available.

response.title: Imparatul Romanilor Hotel
response.subTitle: Hotel Împăratul Romanilor
response.description: Refined hotel dating from 1555, offering a restaurant, an indoor pool & a gym, plus free breakfast.
response.hotelDescription:
In the historic town center, and a 12-minute walk from Sibiu Central Railway Station, this elegant hotel dating from 1555 is 2 minutes' walk from the Brukenthal National Museum and 4 minutes on foot from the Gothic Sibiu Lutheran Cathedral.
 Individually decorated rooms with antique-style furnishings feature Wi-Fi access, cable TV and minibars.
 Breakfast is included. Other amenities consist of a polished restaurant, a gym and an indoor pool, along with a spa area offering a sauna and massage services.

response.title: Hotel Cindrel
response.description: Simple rooms & suites in a relaxed hotel featuring an indoor heated pool, a sauna & a restaurant.
response.hotelDescription:
Surrounded by a forest, this laid-back hotel in a mountain resort is 5 km from the Partia Oncesti ski area and 33 km from Sibiu International Airport.
 Simple rooms feature free Wi-Fi, flat-screen TVs and minibars. Suites come with living rooms. Some quarters have balconies that provide views of the forest or the ski area.
 An informal restaurant offers open-air dining. There's a relaxed bar. Other amenities include a gym, an indoor heated pool and a sauna, as well as facilities for billiards and table tennis. Quad and mountain bike rentals are offered, as are massages.
